{"type": "article", "id": 22232, "title": "给蜡烛和香水找个好气氛，看看纽约这家店", "description": "它连接了工作室和展示间，生产和消费。", "date": "2016-02-15T19:00:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 117, "name": "纽约"}, {"id": 15257, "name": "Joya"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 102, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703122316RuACPQdg6JwqUrG2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://joyastudio.com/#\">Joya </a>是纽约布鲁克林一家香水设计工作室，成立于 2006 年。他们后来发展了蜡烛、香皂、熏香等多个项目，擅长手工制作有艺术感的产品，比如将蜡烛放在大理石杯子里，让大理石的天然纹路赋予蜡烛奢华与厚重。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031223110uHCx8DsBw1nULy6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122311o4XxTpu12LW9cyZ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56037736\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>Joya 的门店设计邀请同在纽约的设计工作室Taylor and Miller Architecture and Design。他们想要在生产工作室旁边建立一个正式、干净而优雅的零售空间。</p>\n<p>店内的展示部分在几张悬挂的铁皮上，由铁管从天花板上吊下来。中间开了一些方形的口，连接着盒子一样的凹槽，蜡烛、香水等展示品就放在这些凹槽内。</p>\n<p>正面铺上了一层橡木板，盒子式的凹槽内装有 LED 灯，橙色的光线正好打在产品上，就像在建筑表面开了一些小窗，非常温馨居家。</p>\n<p>背面却依然维持了黑色铁皮的原样。后面的背景也是黑色的，衬托出黄色灯光的温暖，暗示这些产品就是为家居生活多一分温暖的点缀。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122312b1huYf8BQFnEzwHS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122312bfMjHw5hsaxBr428.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122313d204Hwinebj9MAgh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122313g0LZplwDIecftrzM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122313YrhBM7KwVXzRGOcd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>展示区的背后是加工的地方，透过铁皮之间的缝隙或绕道其后面都可以看到。</p>\n<p>设计者称，“零售空间是连接生产和消费的，这两部分都被看似神圣、干净的门店隔离开了。”铁皮本身就隐喻了背后的工艺，它是粗糙的，未完成的，而它的另一侧则是精致的，就是产品本身。<a href=\"https://www.net-a-porter.com/Shop/Designers/Joya?pn=1&amp;npp=60&amp;image_view=product&amp;dScroll=0\">这里是 Joya 的购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122315mTQnBua5CXRi1OEj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122315l5U4m3CYZoFR2dIk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122315MpgZdLnmGekRvwlV.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2016/02/11/taylor-and-miller-architecture-design-retail-candle-factory-showroom-interior-brooklyn-usa/\"> dezeen</a></p>\n\n\n"}